data.description: Welcome Home! Beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 1/2 bath Turnberry floor plan with a gorgeous lake view is move in ready. This open, airy floor plan welcomes you with a spacious living room/dining room combo complete with gas fireplace and bay window! The kitchen is a dream with fresh cabinetry/countertops and all electric appliances. Upstairs you will find a huge master suite with a large walk in closet and master bath complete with separate shower and whirlpool tub. Two additional spacious bedrooms accompany the master suite on the upper level with their own private bath. The lower level is a blank slate complete with egress window and roughed-in plumbing for your dream entertaining space and/or another private guest suite to come to life!
